=Description=

“The Open Design School is a movement, a school of thought and a virtual institution which advocates design education in the spirit of open source and connected intellectual and creative generosity. We are asking like-minded creatives who are passionate about open education in the art and design sector to come forward and be part of a revolution. We are calling for authors, bloggers, designers, developers, graduates, students, professionals and academics to help us transform the way designers are being trained. Let’s redesign and open up Design Education, together. “

